verbose_text: Thyroid stimulating hormone XREF_BIBR and various compounds such as retinoic acid XREF_BIBR, valporic acid XREF_BIBR, the PPAR gamma agonist Troglitazone XREF_BIBR, the PI3K inhibitor LY294002 XREF_BIBR, and the heat-shock protein inhibitor Tanespimycin XREF_BIBR were reported to elevate NIS protein levels by up-regulating NIS gene expression XREF_BIBR.
